### UI Navigation Pattern (Apple-Inspired)

Ferni uses the Apple navigation pattern:

1. **Settings Menu** → Right-side slide-in panel (for navigation)
2. **Content/Detail Views** → Centered floating modals (for actual content)

```typescript
// ❌ NEVER use centered modal for navigation menu
// ❌ NEVER use side panels for content/detail views

// ✅ Menu slides in from right
.menu-panel {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  right: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  transform: translateX(100%);  // Slide in from right
}

// ✅ Content opens as centered modal
.content-modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
```

### Modal Pattern (Required for all content dialogs)

```typescript
// ✅ Brand-compliant modal structure
`<div class="modal-overlay">
  <div class="modal-backdrop"></div>  <!-- blur backdrop -->
  <div class="modal-card">
    <header>
      <span class="eyebrow">SECTION NAME</span>
      <h2 class="title">Human-readable title</h2>
      <button class="close-btn" aria-label="Close">
        ${LUCIDE_CLOSE_ICON}
      </button>
    </header>
    <div class="content">...</div>
  </div>
</div>`;
```

### Required CSS Variables for Modals

```css
.modal-backdrop {
  background: rgba(44, 37, 32, 0.4); /* Warm overlay */
  backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.modal-card {
  background: var(--color-background-elevated);
  border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-2xl);
}
```

### Toast Pattern (Required for all notifications)

```typescript
// ✅ Brand-compliant toast - small, centered pill
import { toast } from '../ui/toast.ui.js';

toast.success('Saved!');
toast.info('Updated');
toast.warning('Check your input');
toast.error('Something went wrong');
```

### Toast Rules - MANDATORY

```typescript
// ❌ NEVER - Corner positioning
position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px;  // Enterprise software vibes

// ✅ ALWAYS - Centered pill
position: fixed;
bottom: 80px;
left: 50%;
transform: translateX(-50%);
border-radius: var(--radius-full);  // Pill shape
padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);

// ❌ NEVER - Complex toasts with icons and titles
`<div class="toast">
  <svg>✓</svg>
  <div class="title">Success!</div>
  <div class="message">Your changes have been saved successfully</div>
  <button class="close">×</button>
</div>`

// ✅ ALWAYS - Simple text only
`<div class="ferni-toast">Saved!</div>`
```

### Toast Timing

| Type    | Duration | Message Style     |
| ------- | -------- | ----------------- |
| Info    | 2.5s     | Short phrase      |
| Success | 2.5s     | Single word       |
| Warning | 2.5s     | Brief warning     |
| Error   | 4s       | Clear but concise |

### Brand Compliance Checklist - MANDATORY

Before submitting ANY UI code, verify ALL items:

**Colors:**

- [ ] No purple, violet, or cool colors used
- [ ] All colors use CSS variables (--color-_, --persona-_)
- [ ] Accent colors use persona's sage green, not purple
- [ ] Dark theme uses warm browns, not cool grays

**Icons:**

- [ ] NO emoji anywhere in UI code (💜 ❌)
- [ ] All icons are Lucide SVG format
- [ ] Icons use 2px stroke weight, rounded corners
- [ ] Icon color uses currentColor or CSS variable

**Layout:**

- [ ] Modals/dialogs are centered (not side panels)
- [ ] Has backdrop with blur effect
- [ ] Animates with scale/fade (not slide)
- [ ] Close button in top-right with Lucide X icon

**Typography:**

- [ ] Uses eyebrow pattern for section labels
- [ ] Headlines use Plus Jakarta Sans (--font-display)
- [ ] Body text uses Inter (--font-body)
- [ ] Proper hierarchy: eyebrow → title → tagline → body

**Copy/Voice:**

- [ ] Language is warm and human (not corporate)
- [ ] Uses "you/your" not "user"
- [ ] Avoids tech jargon
- [ ] Matches brand voice: Warm, Grounded, Wise, Present

**Dark Theme (WCAG AA Compliance REQUIRED):**

- [ ] Tested in both light AND dark themes
- [ ] All text meets WCAG AA contrast (4.5:1 for normal, 3:1 for large)
- [ ] Uses design system text tokens (--color-text-primary/secondary/muted)
- [ ] No hardcoded colors that break in dark mode
- [ ] Fallback colors in CSS use WCAG-compliant values

**Dark Theme Text Hierarchy (on #70605a background):**
| Token | Color | Contrast | Use |
|-------|-------|----------|-----|
| `--color-text-primary` | #faf6f0 | 5.56:1 | Headings, important text |
| `--color-text-secondary` | #f0ebe4 | 5.05:1 | Body text, descriptions |
| `--color-text-muted` | #e8e2da | 4.65:1 | Labels, eyebrows |
| `--color-text-dimmed` | #ddd6cc | 4.15:1 | Large text only (18pt+) |

